Checking genre filter in News

Test Data (genre| article):
 - "Jazz| Kamasi Washington Shares New Song “The Garden Path”: Listen",
 - "Electronic| Watch LCD Soundsystem Perform “Thrills” and “Yr City’s a Sucker” on",
 - "Rap/Hip-Hop| Dave Shares Video for New Song “Starlight”: Watch",
 - "Metal| Rage Against the Machine Delay Start of Reunion Tour",

Case 1:
1) Open page
2) On Nav bar click News
3) Click Genres
4) In pop-up click "Clear All Selected"
5) Fill genre checkbox
6) In pop-up click "Update All"
ER: pop-up closes, page refreshes, showing news about jazz music, field "Showing:" has selected genre tag

Case 2:
1) Open https://pitchfork.com/
2) On Nav bar click News
3) Click Genres
4) In pop-up click "Clear All Selected"
5) Fill genre checkbox
6) In pop-up click "Update All"
ER: pop-up closes, page refreshes and contains articles about the selected genre

Case 3:
1) Open https://pitchfork.com/
2) Click Search button
3) Enter "Kanye"
ER: suggests opens, which have a category. Category Artists has text "Kanye West" first in the array

Case 4:
1) Open https://pitchfork.com/
2) Click Search button
3) Enter "Kanye"
4) Click "Kanye West" in category Artists from suggests
ER: opens page about rapper Kanye West

Case 5:
1) Open https://pitchfork.com/
2) Click Search button
3) Enter in search "Yeesus"
4) Press Enter
ER: opens page with search result. In category Reviews there is article about album "Yeezus"

Case 6:
1) Open https://pitchfork.com/
2) Click Search button
3) Enter in search "Yeesus"
4) Press Enter
ER: opens page with search result. In category Reviews there is article about album "Yeezus"

Case 7:
1) Open https://pitchfork.com/
2) Click Search button
3) Enter in search "Yeesus"
4) Press Enter
ER: opens page with search result. In category Reviews there is article about album "Yeezus"

Case 8:
1) Open https://pitchfork.com/
2) Click Search button
3) Enter in search "SHXCXCHCXSH"
4) Open in suggest first news in category SHXCXCHCXSH
ER: article opens, article include tag SHXCXCHCXSH

Case 9:
1) Open https://pitchfork.com/
2) Click Reviews on the top bar
3) Open menu Best New Albums
ER: open page, include header "Best new albums", red "best" label and list of albums

Case 10:
1) Open https://pitchfork.com/
2) Click on burger
3) Open UNDER THE INFLUENCES on Video category
ER: page opens, page include video block




